</p></section><section id="GUID-4602A6D6-56F1-4F5E-B77A-B250D42FC0BC" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Background info</b> </title><p class="- topic/p "> The determination of the rotation around the Z-axis (Rz) is determined by measuring the distance in X-position of the left and right side of the printheads. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">In case the difference is out of range this warning is raised. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">In most cases the indicated printhead is not positioned properly. 
